---
layout: recipe
title: "Bacon-wrapped Chicken Thighs"
image:
tags: dinner

ingredients:
  - skinless, boneless chicken thighs
  - bacon strips
  - 1 tspn chipotle powder
  - 1 tspn smoke paprika
  - 1 tspn onion powder
  - 1/2 tspn cinnamon
  - 1 tspn sea salt

directions:
  - Preheat oven to 375 degrees F
  - Mix spices in small bowl
  - Sprinkle the chicken thighs with 1/2 of spice mixture
  - Wrap each thigh in 2 strips of bacon.
  - Sprinkle remaining mixure with spice mixture
  - Bake for approximately 35 minutes or until temperature reaches 165 F.
---

Practical Paleo pages 232 and 262
